      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, form Ibn Mahboub, from Ali Bin Abu Hamza, from Abu Baseer, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The blood relatives are not guarantors in deliberate (killing), nor confession, nor a reconciliation’."
        ]
